    <item>
      <title>Daily Security News from @trustpath - Apr 18, 2017</title>
      <link>//crypt0.net/daily/daily-trust-news-2017-04-18/</link>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Apr 2017 18:05:01 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>//crypt0.net/daily/daily-trust-news-2017-04-18/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Daily Security news from &lt;a href=&#34;http://twitter.com/trustpath&#34;&gt;@trustpath&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;GMO Payment Gateway submits report over data leakage&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;hellip; and Payment Card Forensics, Inc. The latter investigates security incidents and offers consultation and assessment to prevent data breaches.  &lt;a href=&#34;http://financefeeds.com/gmo-payment-gateway-submits-report-japans-ministry-economy-trade-industry-data-leakage/&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://financefeeds.com/gmo-payment-gateway-submits-report-japans-ministry-economy-trade-industry-data-leakage/&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Showpo settles data &amp;lsquo;theft&amp;rsquo; case against rival&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;According to Deloitte, some 14 per cent of data breaches are perpetrated by disgruntled ex-employees. Commenting on matters unrelated to &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.bendigoadvertiser.com.au/story/4602830/showpo-settles-data-theft-case-against-rival/&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.bendigoadvertiser.com.au/story/4602830/showpo-settles-data-theft-case-against-rival/&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Showpo and Black Swallow settle data theft allegations&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Experts in information security and surveys showed the relevance of employees in data breaches. Managing director of the Information Security Forum &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.ibtimes.com.au/showpo-black-swallow-settle-data-theft-allegations-1550669&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.ibtimes.com.au/showpo-black-swallow-settle-data-theft-allegations-1550669&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;ECMC continues &amp;lsquo;huge task&amp;rsquo; to get computers back online&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In the world of data breaches, health care organizations will be the most targeted business sector, according to a recent report by the credit reporting &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://buffalonews.com/2017/04/17/ecmc-continues-efforts-restore-hospital-computer-functions/&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://buffalonews.com/2017/04/17/ecmc-continues-efforts-restore-hospital-computer-functions/&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Bypassing Sophos Endpoint Protection and Intercept X&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;this video: &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2Xh1_LOKQPI&#34;&gt;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2Xh1_LOKQPI&lt;/a&gt;. How worried &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;https://community.sophos.com/products/intercept/f/feedback/91006/bypassing-sophos-endpoint-protection-and-intercept-x&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;https://community.sophos.com/products/intercept/f/feedback/91006/bypassing-sophos-endpoint-protection-and-intercept-x&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Guidance Software and Lastline Partner for Faster Incident Response&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;New integration combines advanced threat intelligence and endpoint detection and response to reduce the time between detection and triage from &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.businesswire.com/news/home/20170418005271/en/Guidance-Software-Lastline-Partner-Faster-Incident-Response&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.businesswire.com/news/home/20170418005271/en/Guidance-Software-Lastline-Partner-Faster-Incident-Response&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;1.5 million patient records breached in March&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Published in JAMA Internal Medicine, the study found the risk of data breaches is higher at large healthcare facilities and teaching hospitals.  &lt;a href=&#34;http://medcitynews.com/2017/04/million-patient-records-breached-march/&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://medcitynews.com/2017/04/million-patient-records-breached-march/&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Employee Healthcare Data Security Awareness Top Industry Threat&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;When it comes to protecting the organization from potential data breaches, 34 percent of respondents said they use Cyber Threat Intelligence (CTI).  &lt;a href=&#34;http://healthitsecurity.com/news/employee-healthcare-data-security-awareness-top-industry-threat&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://healthitsecurity.com/news/employee-healthcare-data-security-awareness-top-industry-threat&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Infographic: Healthcare Organizations Reluctant to Rush to the Cloud&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The past few years have been tough for the healthcare industry because of large-scale data breaches and pressure from regulatory bodies.  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.pharmiweb.com/pressreleases/pressrel.asp?ROW_ID=215477&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.pharmiweb.com/pressreleases/pressrel.asp?ROW_ID=215477&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;PeoplePoint audit shows 350 data breaches since 2014&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;An audit report has found there were 350 data breaches in two years at PeoplePoint, the centre that provides HR and pensions administration services &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.irishtimes.com/news/ireland/irish-news/peoplepoint-audit-shows-350-data-breaches-since-2014-1.3053317&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.irishtimes.com/news/ireland/irish-news/peoplepoint-audit-shows-350-data-breaches-since-2014-1.3053317&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Almost 1.4b data records compromised in 2016, 44 per second, Gemalto says&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Digital security firm Gemalto asks, &amp;ldquo;Do you know where your data is?&amp;rdquo;, revaling 1,792 disclosed data breaches in 2016 led to almost 1.4 billion data &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.itwire.com/security/77705-almost-1-4b-data-records-compromised-in-2016,-44-per-second,-gemalto-says.html&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.itwire.com/security/77705-almost-1-4b-data-records-compromised-in-2016,-44-per-second,-gemalto-says.html&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
